title: Good Sluts Factory (let it cia mix) [ELECTRONIC]
description:
Kiko & Gino Present

Good Sluts Factory (let it cia mix) Feat. Naommon Noam

Gigolo 164




The best electronic song of all time wasn't on this site yet so here it is.

It's my favorite song of all time, nothing else comes close. I've been listening to it for many years and it still kicks all kinds of ass. It deserves a proper video. This song needs to go viral! If you like it too spread the word. The lyrics don't exist on any site. I personally asked for them from Naommon.
